--- class escape / valid outside class ---
\b\w+\b	: valid
\B\w+\B	: valid
\D+	: valid
\W+	: valid
\S+	: valid
--- class escape / invalid inside class ---
[\b]	:\b and \B are not supported inside a character class at position 1
[\B]	:\b and \B are not supported inside a character class at position 1
[\D]	:\D, \W, \S are not supported inside a character class at position 1
[\W]	:\D, \W, \S are not supported inside a character class at position 1
[\S]	:\D, \W, \S are not supported inside a character class at position 1
[\D\W]	:\D, \W, \S are not supported inside a character class at position 1
